color4 <- c("indeterminate" = "darkgrey", 
           "negative" = "#8B1E3F", 
           "positive" = "#13505B")



cabo <- read.csv ("CABOAERODATA.csv") |> 
  janitor::clean_names() |> 
  filter(indication != "") |> 
  mutate(indication = str_squish(indication)) |> 
  mutate(indication = gsub("Non-small Cell Lung Cancer", "NSCLC", indication), 
           indication = gsub(" Cancer$", "", indication),
           indication = str_squish(indication), 
           date = as.Date(year, "%m/%d/%Y"), 
            year = lubridate::year(date),
           result = tolower(result), 
           participants = as.numeric(gsub("," ,"", participants)), 
           id = row_number()) |> 
   # The following adds 30 days to dates that are overlapping on the timeline
  group_by(indication, phase) |> 
  arrange(date) |> 
  mutate(diff = date - lag(date)) |> 
  mutate(date = if_else(diff <= 30 & (!is.na(diff)), date + ddays(30), date)) |> 
  ungroup()

Figure 1.2

levs2 <- cabo |> 
  count(indication, sort = T) |> 
  pull(indication)





phase_counter <- tibble(phase = rep(list(c("I", "II", "III")), length(levs2)), 
       indication = levs2) |> 
  unnest(phase)


phase_counter2 <-cabo |>
  count(indication, phase) |> 
  full_join(phase_counter, by = c("phase", "indication")) |> 
  # filter(indication == "Bone Metastasis") |> 
  mutate(hasPhase = ifelse(is.na(n), "n", "y"))


fake_phases <- phase_counter2 |> 
  select(-n) |> 
  mutate( dayssince = as.numeric((as.Date("01/01/2010",  "%m/%d/%Y")-(as.Date("01/01/2011",  "%m/%d/%Y")))), 
          result = "fake")



color5 <- c("indeterminate" = "darkgrey", 
           "negative" = "#8B1E3F", 
           "positive" = "#13505B")





cabo_form1 <- cabo |> 
  mutate(enddate = date + 360, 
           dayssince = as.numeric(date-(as.Date("01/01/2011",  "%m/%d/%Y")))) |> 
  bind_rows(fake_phases) |> 
  mutate(indication = factor(indication, levels = levs2), 
         phase = factor(phase, levels = rev(c("I", "II", "III")))) |> 
    arrange(dayssince) |> 
  group_by(indication, phase) |> 
  mutate(id = paste0(indication, "_p", phase, ".", id), 
         id2 = paste0(indication, "_p", phase), 
         id2 = factor(id2))  |> 
  ungroup() |> 
  mutate(size_ = cut_number(participants, n =5)) 




gridz  <- cbind(
bind_rows(rep(
list(tibble(line_start = as.numeric((as.Date("01/01/2011",  "%m/%d/%Y")-(as.Date("01/01/2011",  "%m/%d/%Y")))), 
                line_end = 4745)), nrow(phase_counter))), id2 = levels(cabo_form1$id2)) |> 
  mutate(indication = str_squish(gsub("_.*", "", id2)), 
         phase = gsub(".*_p", "", id2), 
         id2 = factor(id2, levels = levels(cabo_form1$id2)), 
         indication = factor(indication, levels = levels(cabo_form1$indication)))


phase_label <- function(x) {
  #return(gsub(".*_p", "", x))
  r1 <- gsub("III", "3", gsub(".*_p", "", x))
  
  r2 <- gsub("II", "2", r1)
  
  return(gsub("I", "1", r2))
}



fig1.2 <- ggplot() +
    geom_segment(data = gridz, aes(y = id2, yend = id2, x = line_start, xend = line_end, linetype = phase), color = "grey") +
